body:
BREAKING CHANGE: The way to access connectors (NameOfWidget.connect)
and default widgets (NameOfWidget) has changed. You need to update
your imports.

Now:

```js
import {InstantSearch, SearchBox, RangeRatings} from 'react-instantsearch/dom';
import {connectSearchBox} from 'react-instantsearch/connectors';
import {createConnector} from 'react-instantsearch';
```

Before:

```js
import {InstantSearch, SearchBox, Range} from 'react-instantsearch/dom';
// use SearchBox.connect
// use Range.Ratings
```

fixes algolia/react-instantsearch#1454

Ultimately we might have different packages. This will also ease usage
in react-native moving forward.
